HEADWORD: Fucusol
<hw>Fu"cu*sol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Fucus</ets> +
L. <ets>oleum</ets> oil.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>An oily liquid,
resembling, and possibly identical with, furfurol, and obtained from
fucus, and other seaweeds.</def>⟦br⟧
